briefdescription.para: playback rate of the viewer - a value of 1 means realtime
the play, pause, ffwd, etc buttons

detaileddescription.para: Queued command from fast restarts. When the last command was halt/stop/force start/ready, this is nullopt. When the last command was a kickoff setup, this is the kickoff command (a ready command will be sent next).
Technically if we change our team color between setting queued_command_ and actually sending it, the restart will be for the wrong team, but this really never matters.
